title: Vegan Sweet Tooth
description: Vegan chef and baker Giancarlo offers custom cakes and cooking classes. He specializes in making allergy-friendly cakes and sells them at area markets - check webpage for latest updates. As of Oct 2015: Saturday 10am-6pm at Hackney Homemade Market in Hackney Central; Sunday 11am-4pm at Chatsworth Market in Chatsworth Rd.
